# Generated render artifacts (MP4/WebM/etc.) are large binaries — kept locally, not in git.
# The folder, this ignore, and README.md ARE tracked so the convention is documented.
*.mp4
*.webm
*.mov
*.gif
# the newscast/score script saved next to each render (the exact input used to generate it) —
# a local convenience artifact paired with the (also-ignored) video, not source of truth.
*.newscast.json
*.score.json
# demodu scene-DSL script saved next to each recorder-produced demo (same convention).
*.scene.json
# synced custom-recorder script paired with its demo
*.record.mjs
!README.md
